            This is intended as a companion torrent to the recently released
            "Book One" edition ( <a href=" https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/11719569" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/11719569</a>  ),

            upload. "Book One" includes a bunch of bonus materials, which are
            however almost entirely distinct from these ones. The reason for
            the absence of any "Volume 1" extras is that those were limited
            to a single page (the back cover), which happened to be among the
            minority to be included in the new edition as well. Enjoy!
